Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:71473,75811}{\i1}September 2, 1870.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.81,0:01:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:75811,79398}{\i1}Prussian troops defeated\Nthe French army in Sedan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:79398,81859}{\i1}and began to march\Nto the French capital, Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:81859,84403}{\i1}The danger was imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:90576,92661}{\i1}Do you expect us to die here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:92661,94913}{\i1}We're going back to protect Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:94913,96665}{\i1}We still have Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.98,0:02:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119980,121273}We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121273,122733}This is Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122733,123609}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123609,126487}It's the lights of Paris.\NWe're finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127321,128072}Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128072,131200}This is Captain Andréa.\NThis man needs immediate medical help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131200,131825}Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138499,141043}Life's full of irony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141043,143420}Just a moment\Nafter we made it…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144463,145631}Andréa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146924,148217}Is that you, Andréa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148217,149551}Victor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150928,152054}Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152429,153889}Andréa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153889,154848}Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154848,156100}Andréa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156100,157726}I knew you'd be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157976,161772}You're not a man that\Nwould go down so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161772,163357}I'm glad to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163649,166360}As long as I have Paris,\NI will not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166360,169321}I won't give Paris to Prussia,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169321,172408}I came back\Nto defend our capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172741,175494}Let's defend it together.\NThis is our city.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175869,178288}The honor of France is at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:02:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178288,179331}Let's do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180457,182167}I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183043,184420}With the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184420,185504}Yeah.
