Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.77,0:25:03.69,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1498774,1503696}La la la, our song\Nreaches across the stream
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.69,0:25:08.86,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1503696,1508868}and echoes in the green mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.86,0:25:14.20,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1508868,1514206}Let's run with all our might
